	<div class="cs-panel">
	<h3><a href="/casestudy/case-1-patient-risk-pre-diabetes" title="Case 1: Patient At Risk For Pre-Diabetes">Case 1: Patient At Risk For Pre-Diabetes</a></h3>

	
	<div class="meta">
				<div class="terms">Tags: <span  class="taxonomy_term_179 first"><a href="/category/tags/lifestyle-changes" rel="tag" title="">lifestyle changes</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_180"><a href="/category/tags/metformin" rel="tag" title="">metformin</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_181"><a href="/category/tags/prediabetes" rel="tag" title="">prediabetes</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_183"><a href="/category/tags/thiazolidinediones-tzds" rel="tag" title="">thiazolidinediones (TZDs)</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_184 last"><a href="/category/tags/weight" rel="tag" title="">weight</a></span></div>
		</div>

	
	<div class="content">
		<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-casestudy-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="/casestudy/case-1-patient-risk-pre-diabetes" class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small imagecache-linked imagecache-casestudy_small_linked"><img src="http://www.betacellsindiabetes.org/sites/default/files/imagecache/casestudy_small/casestudyimages/case-study-1_0.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small" width="112" height="92" /></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p><span>A 45-year-old African American man with a history of obesity and hypercholesteremia has been under your care for the past three years.&nbsp;He has a family history of both T2DM (type 2 diabetes mellitus) and cardiovascular disease but no history of cardiovascular events.</span></p>
	</div>
	
