          <li class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even"><div id="node-187" class="node type-case_study teaser">


	<div class="cs-panel">
	<h3><a href="/casestudy/case-2-metformin-fails-t2dm-patient" title="Case 2: Metformin Fails in T2DM Patient">Case 2: Metformin Fails in T2DM Patient</a></h3>

	
	<div class="meta">
				<div class="terms">Tags: <span  class="taxonomy_term_175 first"><a href="/category/tags/dpp-4-inhibitors" rel="tag" title="">DPP-4 inhibitors</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_176"><a href="/category/tags/glp-1-agonists" rel="tag" title="">GLP-1 agonists</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_177"><a href="/category/tags/glycemic-control" rel="tag" title="">glycemic control</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_180"><a href="/category/tags/metformin" rel="tag" title="">metformin</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_182"><a href="/category/tags/sulfonylureas-sus" rel="tag" title="">sulfonylureas (SUs)</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_183"><a href="/category/tags/thiazolidinediones-tzds" rel="tag" title="">thiazolidinediones (TZDs)</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_184 last"><a href="/category/tags/weight" rel="tag" title="">weight</a></span></div>
		</div>

	
	<div class="content">
		<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-casestudy-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="/casestudy/case-2-metformin-fails-t2dm-patient" class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small imagecache-linked imagecache-casestudy_small_linked"><img src="http://www.betacellsindiabetes.org/sites/default/files/imagecache/casestudy_small/casestudyimages/case-study-2_0.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small" width="112" height="92" /></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p><span>A 55-year old Caucasian woman has been under your care for three years.&nbsp;Eighteen months ago you diagnosed her with type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).</span> <span>She has a history of mild hypertension, hypercholesteremia, and retinopathy. </span></p>
	</div>
	
