	<div class="cs-panel">
	<h3><a href="/casestudy/case-3-two-orals-fail-t2dm-patient" title="Case 3: Two Orals Fail in T2DM Patient">Case 3: Two Orals Fail in T2DM Patient</a></h3>

	
	<div class="meta">
				<div class="terms">Tags: <span  class="taxonomy_term_176 first"><a href="/category/tags/glp-1-agonists" rel="tag" title="">GLP-1 agonists</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_177"><a href="/category/tags/glycemic-control" rel="tag" title="">glycemic control</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_178"><a href="/category/tags/insulin-therapy" rel="tag" title="">insulin therapy</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_180"><a href="/category/tags/metformin" rel="tag" title="">metformin</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_182"><a href="/category/tags/sulfonylureas-sus" rel="tag" title="">sulfonylureas (SUs)</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_183"><a href="/category/tags/thiazolidinediones-tzds" rel="tag" title="">thiazolidinediones (TZDs)</a></span>, <span  class="taxonomy_term_184 last"><a href="/category/tags/weight" rel="tag" title="">weight</a></span></div>
		</div>

	
	<div class="content">
		<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-casestudy-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="/casestudy/case-3-two-orals-fail-t2dm-patient" class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small imagecache-linked imagecache-casestudy_small_linked"><img src="http://www.betacellsindiabetes.org/sites/default/files/imagecache/casestudy_small/casestudyimages/case-study-3(5).jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-casestudy_small" width="112" height="92" /></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p><span>A 63-year-old Hispanic woman with type 2 diabetes (T2DM) has been under your care for ten years and she was diagnosed with T2DM six years ago.</span> <span>In addition to long-standing hypertension and hypercholesteremia, she has a BMI (body-mass index) of 31 kg/m2&nbsp;as well as a family history of cardiovascular disease.</span></p>
	</div>
	
